Actors
User: Represents anyone using the system to make bookings or manage their account.
System: Represents the booking system itself.
Use Cases
Register: User creates a new account.
Login: User logs into the system.
View Available Slots: User views the available booking slots.
Book Slot: User books an available slot.
Cancel Booking: User cancels an existing booking.
View Booking History: User views their booking history.
Create Zoom Meeting: User creates a new Zoom meeting.
View Zoom Meetings: User views their Zoom meetings.
Delete Zoom Meeting: User deletes a Zoom meeting.
Use Case Relationships
Include Relationship:

Book Slot includes View Available Slots.
Cancel Booking includes View Booking History.
Extend Relationship:

Create Zoom Meeting extends Book Slot.
